Hi Jeff,

Interesting. As I said, I haven&#39;t used one yet.

I just have a lot of suspicion about devices that generate phonemes as 
opposed to actual sounds received. I&#39;m sure some spirits can make them 
produce messages but they could also produce something out of random 
sounds. That&#39;s what I&#39;d be worried about. Might sort of come out like 
James Joyce&#39;s Ulysses.
:-)

Zack

